H. Bruce Humberstone https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/H._Bruce_Humberstone 0 H. Bruce "Lucky" Humberstone (November 18, 1901 – October 11, 1984) was a movie actor (as a child), a script clerk, an assistant director, working with directors such as King Vidor, Edmund Goulding and Allan Dwan and, ultimately, a director.
